OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA clear
OL,6,Fnight to come with high cloud in the
OL,7,Fwest. Patchy mist and fog developing
OL,8,Fin prone spots to the east.
OL,9,FTemperatures dropping soon after dusk
OL,10,Fnear freezing in some rural spots with
OL,11,Fa grass frost developing in places.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FAnother bright and sunny day
OL,14,Fto start the weekend. Any low cloud
OL,15,Falong southern coasts should quickly
OL,16,Fburn back, but will feel very warm in
OL,17,Fthe light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
